.name
Expose
.author
John Russell 
.source
Includes source in C.
.description
Program which will automatically cause all screen drag bars and screen
depth-arrangers to become exposed.  Sends a message to windows which
obscure the screen drag bars, asking them to move down a pixel, and also to
become smaller if necessary.  
